03. Not a number for q op == and range, lower limit
===================================================
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
Date: REGEX(.*)
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 65

{
    "description": "invalid range: types mixed",
    "error": "BadRequest"
}


